@DATABASE "After The War Part 1"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - A - After The War Part 1"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - A
                   ====================================

                           After The War Part 1
                           ====================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====
            
@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(48950,0)"}         49001,0
@{"Infinite Time  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(55539,0)"}         55539,0
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52364,60)"}         52364,60
@{"View End Code  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(48826,0)"}         48826,0
@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(48819,255)"}         48819,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
